{"tid":1285334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【治癒街站】一齊貼D治癒圖／片幫大家心靈療傷","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T08:54:17.000Z","uid":70786,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7b659b6317ee05c9da801a56c5319bc9d696592d","tid":1285334,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:01:57.000Z","msg":"大家請幫幫手！！！<br />\n近日真係太多好沉重嘅新聞同資訊<br />\n好多手足都可能因為咁出現抑鬱症狀<br />\n大家唔可以俾D負面情緒吞沒佢地<br />\n希望各位可以貼D治癒圖／片<br />\n將佢地救翻出嚟<br />\n先貼為敬！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z7PlUGbsXlQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ7PlUGbsXlQ&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=232c0d0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z7PlUGbsXlQ</a><br />\n貼之前請預覽，確定已經嵌入片段，方便手足觀賞<br />\nYoutube片按分享再copy&amp;paste就可以<br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得出嚟發夢，身邊雖然都係戴住口罩嘅陌生人<br />\n但係有佢地係身邊，你都會感到無比安全<br />\n佢地窩心嘅舉動，為你帶嚟溫暖同動力<br />\n請大家記住呢班同路人，一路走來，你從不孤單<br />\n「世界很遼闊，只要活下去，一定會遇到美好的事。」<br />\n<br />\n請勿只推唔貼，希望每個回覆都可以帶嚟治癒力量！"},{"pid":"4f939167388a2abe4e422320b63454cce4e4ffae","tid":1285334,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t5MQVBaqVkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft5MQVBaqVkA&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=78cbc385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t5MQVBaqVkA</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd2cceef443f726aba5f1c05b9b819eb1908c10","tid":1285334,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0009ad3190b84ef7ce98ccff89c975f468ad34b","tid":1285334,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:03:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"h